claim.claim-text:
8. An adapter plate for attaching a standard adapter to a non-standard wall, the adapter plate comprising:
a front and a back and an aperture therethrough for receiving at least a portion of a standard adapter;
a footprint receiving portion for receiving at least a portion of an adapter footprint;
a flange receiving portion for receiving an adapter flange; and
an attachment feature for attaching the adapter plate to a non-standard wall.
